## 3. ENUMS

### `skill_level` (games and profiles)
Valid values: `all`, `beginner`, `intermediate`, `advanced`
DEPRECATED: `tournament` — do not use; causes 22P02 on RPC calls

### `booking_status` (stored as TEXT in bookings.status)
Valid values: `confirmed`, `waitlisted`, `cancelled`, `pending_payment`
Note: PG enum exists as `booking_status`. When comparing in PL/pgSQL, cast to text first:
`v_booking.status::text != 'cancelled'` — direct enum comparison with string literal raises error 22P02.

### `payment_method` (bookings.payment_method, TEXT)
Valid values: `"stripe"`, `"admin"`, `"cash"`, `"credits"`, NULL
DB CHECK constraint enforced (migration `20260430_bookings_payment_method_constraint.sql`) — any other value is rejected.

| Value | Meaning | Who writes it |
|---|---|---|
| `"stripe"` | Card or Apple Pay via Stripe | `confirmPendingBooking`, `updateBookingPaymentMethod` |
| `"admin"` | Owner/admin manually added player | `ownerCreateBooking`, `updateBookingPaymentMethod` |
| `"cash"` | Admin-recorded cash payment at check-in | `updateBookingPaymentMethod` |
| `"credits"` | Credits-only booking (no Stripe PI) | `confirmPendingBooking` when no Stripe PI |
| NULL | Free game, no payment collected | free game booking path |

**NEVER write any other value** — the DB CHECK will reject it. The legacy value `"free"` was normalised to NULL in the same migration and no longer exists.

### `game_format` (games.game_format, TEXT)
DB CHECK constraint enforced (migration `20260429_normalize_game_format.sql`).
Valid values: `"open_play"`, `"random"`, `"round_robin"`, `"king_of_court"`, `"dupr_king_of_court"`

**BANNED**: `"ladder"` — was a legacy alias for `king_of_court`. Normalized out of the DB. **Never write `"ladder"` to the DB or accept it as a valid wire value.** Display labels live in the UI layer only.

### `cancellation_reason` (bookings.cancellation_reason, TEXT)
Valid values: `"player_cancelled"`, `"admin_cancelled"`, `"game_cancelled"`

### `credit transaction reason` (credit_transactions.reason, TEXT)
Valid values: `"booking_applied"`, `"cancellation_refund"`, `"admin_adjustment"`

### `subscription_tier` (clubs.subscription_tier, TEXT)
Valid values: `"free"`, `"starter"`, `"pro"`, `"enterprise"`

### `subscription status` (club_subscriptions.status, TEXT)
Valid values: `"incomplete"`, `"active"`, `"past_due"`, `"canceled"`

